ExtendibleHashingScheme

Class Directory

  • java.lang.Object
    • ExtendibleHashingScheme.Directory

  • public class Directory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the Directory Structure of the Extendible Hashing Scheme. This class has a list of records that maps the Global Hash Value to the Bucket. All the buckets of the Scheme are a part of the Data File.
